A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Splash Festivals; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, founded by Frances Schube and Cindy Flynn, Splash Festivals specializes in
3 producing vibrant and engaging art events that promote the cities they represent, bringing
4 together artisans, visitors, and local businesses in a mutual celebration of creativity and
5 community; and
6 WHEREAS, since its incorporation in 2009, Splash Festivals has organized and produced
7 such outstanding experiences as the Brookhaven Cherry Blossom Festival, the Acworth Art
8 Fest, the Chamblee Art Fest, the Dunwoody Art Festival, the Alpharetta Arts Streetfest, the
9 Norcross Art Splash Festival, and the Johns Creek Arts Festival; and
10 WHEREAS, the Norcross Art Splash Festival, one of the largest annual events in the City
11 of Norcross, first began in 2004 and has since grown into a major attraction, drawing large
12 crowds from both within and outside the city while also supporting local businesses and
13 fostering economic activity in downtown Norcross; and
14 WHEREAS, the success of the Norcross Art Splash Festival is made possible through the
15 dedication of more than 100 volunteers, many of whom are Norcross citizens, who
